{"tid":140740,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"未來戰爭步兵仲佔唔佔到一席","createTime":"2017-03-02T11:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T06:07:17.000Z","uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5bbd21021d0edbb18156030289509f8265ffd1d9","tid":140740,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:47:47.000Z","msg":"以前打仗靠人海戰術<br />\n士兵欠缺訓練<br />\n裝備參差<br />\n死傷大<br />\n但而家戰術越黎越先進<br />\n偷聽無線電乜都有<br />\n裝備越黎越勁，可以殺敵於千里之外<br />\n唔使再好似以前咁靠地面部隊打生打死先打得贏<br />\n各國依家都積極裁軍<br />\n步兵係咪好快會成為歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a80a3fa58e5e7475612ec75521f4b8cbb90d08","tid":140740,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"MGS<br />\n要精兵"},{"pid":"1a07a5d73993f56e8fe1d97817aa894f4516d8c9","tid":140740,"uid":54988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:55:12.000Z","msg":"應該會用無人駕駛機械代替 遙距控制<br />\n所以邊個話打機無用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353a5d126496a0ff4cc068d7ac8ae16335f01ac5","tid":140740,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:56:28.000Z","msg":"佔到，做靶lor"},{"pid":"867613dc62abaf7ce080458b1b8102a228cb7bf2","tid":140740,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:56:30.000Z","msg":"睇高達就知"},{"pid":"4687f64c4ae8a90e9bbcc6e86860d6410c24ad47","tid":140740,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"隻高達係地面行算唔算步兵"},{"pid":"5eb9c4220f63b7b4892bf08bec11bc5afa2f1117","tid":140740,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T11:58:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>MGS<br />\n要精兵</blockquote><br />\n但依家一支導彈做到既野可能比得起一隊精兵<br />\n依家好多武器都係向緊呢方面發展<br />\n咩無人機個d<br />\n遲下可能連sniper都比人取締埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc42e4868a9c589123cb54cbec5d260c9f3ea57","tid":140740,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佔到，做靶lor</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家d衛星先進到可以睇到離地面兩米既野<br />\n一隊兵咁行法好易暴露<br />\n同做活靶冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe61f4be6c5fc4a9497dc766bbbe2a6929740e1","tid":140740,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"以後得經濟戰爭 啲軍備用黎兇人"},{"pid":"bd44d4d59c7bd86de8695b40989ded45a65c6a18","tid":140740,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇高達就知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n08ms team  步兵可以打渣古"},{"pid":"d4e6e1d67b248bb04bda78125d67cdae085c8c4a","tid":140740,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:06:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以後得經濟戰爭 啲軍備用黎兇人</blockquote><br />\n好似以前冷戰咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一味得個整字<br />\n但又冇用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd軍火都唔知貢獻左幾多稅俾政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e547509f369dd2596de6a52de52db43d5d0b5240","tid":140740,"uid":35702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:07:14.000Z","msg":"可能會有一大個廠房<br />\n個個係入面打機遙控無人機咁去打仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2ba96d6035f052d8ad57f3f7013dc339072a7a","tid":140740,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能會有一大個廠房<br />\n個個係入面打機遙控無人機咁去打仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nender's game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9e728cd8f7245c884ecc96c05063aee8008e82","tid":140740,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:08:11.000Z","msg":"好難無地面部隊<br />\n始終係人打人"},{"pid":"bf515e175c9a63797ea18ec40c80a5aefc22665e","tid":140740,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:09:45.000Z","msg":"建議以後打war game 決勝負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e466e7c28a51b2057eba5fb173daae587eae43b","tid":140740,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:10:05.000Z","msg":"你要佔領就要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8468f4ccfc6902162e624503069eed8c3f4e8dba","tid":140740,"uid":36715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:12:27.000Z","msg":"無步兵點佔一個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通你搵坦克車爆門捉人？<br />\n唔通你搵戰機派糧救援？<br />\nUC 打阿巴奧最後咪又係步兵進入基地，唔通靠高達縮細拉咗基連咩<br />\n即使係後援都係步兵，唔通設計一部精密但易壞嘅機械去修理另一樣精密但易壞嘅機械咩"},{"pid":"9443bc482c723e9ae07d82436c9a29fc9f450eeb","tid":140740,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要佔領就要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e563f243b213124d13fb3cee5f4cb49d2a71d054","tid":140740,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T12:18:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無步兵點佔一個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通你搵坦克車爆門捉人？<br />\n唔通你搵戰機派糧救援？<br />\nUC 打阿巴奧最後咪又係步兵進入基地，唔通靠高達縮細拉咗基連咩<br />\n即使係後援都係步兵，唔通設計一部精密但易壞嘅機械去修理另一樣精密但易壞嘅機械咩</blockquote><br />\n清點睇依家美國，法國研究既單兵作戰system"},{"pid":"821ddfcba0cf67e63c6bef7e9916eb695f7d3adb","tid":140740,"uid":36715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無步兵點佔一個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通你搵坦克車爆門捉人？<br />\n唔通你搵戰機派糧救援？<br />\nUC 打阿巴奧最後咪又係步兵進入基地，唔通靠高達縮細拉咗基連咩<br />\n即使係後援都係步兵，唔通設計一部精密但易壞嘅機械去修理另一樣精密但易壞嘅機械咩</blockquote><br />\n清點睇依家美國，法國研究既單兵作戰system</blockquote><br />\n你見依家係咩聲氣就知，都搞咗成十幾年<br />\n依家成效未明，又重又啊乍，明明一部iPhone做到嘅嘢就要掛十幾樣嘢上身，好多功能係咪好似宣傳一樣把炮又係唔知<br />\n之前駐阿富汗嘅特種部隊以至正規部隊都盡量少帶嘢，連軍鞋都嫌重要換運動鞋你就知，未來係追求輕而唔係重<br />\n<br />\n應該係"},{"pid":"7b479aa99656646fbe67efb1b5dc2924b58c3710","tid":140740,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/terminator/images/2/24/Terminator.gif/revision/latest?cb=20080316165338\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fterminator%2Fimages%2F2%2F24%2FTerminator.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20080316165338&h=39173b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://tropeanddagger.files.wordpress.com/2015/07/crawl-gif.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftropeanddagger.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F07%2Fcrawl-gif.gif&h=c8b8b5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://majesticlizard.tripod.com/Terminators.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmajesticlizard.tripod.com%2FTerminators.gif&h=a4480c0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03282062a221a46dd5c72e3956c2a09eaaf618f9","tid":140740,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"步兵一定有用，但會係機械人（如果夠靈活）"},{"pid":"e0c984e100a869b8745d3c90c35ff90889ec96b7","tid":140740,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要佔領就要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果機械人去到好輕同靈活果陣就冇需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869e9465ae5661243722ffdd2713431233596872","tid":140740,"uid":33040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:12:32.000Z","msg":"一定係無人機/機械人"},{"pid":"b0d729a58c4f267f6591883c892d2752e6c24c46","tid":140740,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:13:04.000Z","msg":"未來會係無人機同機械人之戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d259b632d2a1b632cfa31620cf3726f22317ffb","tid":140740,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:14:32.000Z","msg":"應該會越來越重要，想象下好似香港呢d高樓林立既城市，你要唔摧毀座城又要佔領，自然需要步兵去逐層逐戶去清除敵軍，尤其是未來非對稱戰爭會成爲主流<br />\n外骨骼裝甲既普及，又提升左步兵面對坦克同直升機既生存能力<br />\n<br />\n另一個趨勢係無人機，但係無人機普及到生産成本可以低過步兵之前，無人機好大機會係由兵員不足既發達國家獨佔技術。好似印度，中國呢d人口膨脹既國家，人命實在太唔值錢，應該仲會相當依賴步兵，更加唔使講有一班信仰極度狂熱既宗教原教旨主義分子直頭視死如歸。"},{"pid":"c51dad33a7ebf80459aa0882de69dc284263f7d7","tid":140740,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:18:28.000Z","msg":"如果有第四次世界大戰，步兵一定係主流<br />\n根據愛因斯坦說法"},{"pid":"7051ef17554f8c09670f3ba0036920081e091592","tid":140740,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T10:02:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果有第四次世界大戰，步兵一定係主流<br />\n根據愛因斯坦說法</blockquote><br />\n我不知道第三次世界大戰用甚麼打 但第四次世界大戰會用木捧跟石頭"},{"pid":"e134965033b1f125d1737aca714e201d8ca79bd1","tid":140740,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:41:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果有第四次世界大戰，步兵一定係主流<br />\n根據愛因斯坦說法</blockquote><br />\n我不知道第三次世界大戰用甚麼打 但第四次世界大戰會用木捧跟石頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係 魚蛋革命 已經係打緊第四次世界大戰<br />\n<br />\n示威者(石頭) vs 警察(棍)"},{"pid":"4dff71618040b42e0251aead5dac835defd1de86","tid":140740,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:47:40.000Z","msg":"用電競代替打仗"},{"pid":"103ad3c276efd4559c668eaedfb597885dfc02c7","tid":140740,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:54:55.000Z","msg":"步兵係一種政治工具"},{"pid":"a3084f41ab18dd9721646adce958584c3e93c876","tid":140740,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:10:03.000Z","msg":"到底你指既步兵 包唔包 機械人型既步兵先 定單純指人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你要佔領 而唔係完全消滅一個地方 就一定要步兵<br />\n只係用人類定機械呢種模式既分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e39d74f8750a66598cb094420ea5c1de14a83a4","tid":140740,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你要佔領就要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果機械人去到好輕同靈活果陣就冇需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人型機械人根本不切實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75679d296d7adf4e31c9102971aaf94807006a6","tid":140740,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該會越來越重要，想象下好似香港呢d高樓林立既城市，你要唔摧毀座城又要佔領，自然需要步兵去逐層逐戶去清除敵軍，尤其是未來非對稱戰爭會成爲主流<br />\n外骨骼裝甲既普及，又提升左步兵面對坦克同直升機既生存能力<br />\n<br />\n另一個趨勢係無人機，但係無人機普及到生産成本可以低過步兵之前，無人機好大機會係由兵員不足既發達國家獨佔技術。好似印度，中國呢d人口膨脹既國家，人命實在太唔值錢，應該仲會相當依賴步兵，更加唔使講有一班信仰極度狂熱既宗教原教旨主義分子直頭視死如歸。</blockquote><br />\n步兵點重甲都唔會夠坦克直昇機嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13208df970ceb91a63f0881c0130771f0825c43","tid":140740,"uid":36715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該會越來越重要，想象下好似香港呢d高樓林立既城市，你要唔摧毀座城又要佔領，自然需要步兵去逐層逐戶去清除敵軍，尤其是未來非對稱戰爭會成爲主流<br />\n外骨骼裝甲既普及，又提升左步兵面對坦克同直升機既生存能力<br />\n<br />\n另一個趨勢係無人機，但係無人機普及到生産成本可以低過步兵之前，無人機好大機會係由兵員不足既發達國家獨佔技術。好似印度，中國呢d人口膨脹既國家，人命實在太唔值錢，應該仲會相當依賴步兵，更加唔使講有一班信仰極度狂熱既宗教原教旨主義分子直頭視死如歸。</blockquote><br />\n步兵點重甲都唔會夠坦克直昇機嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔需要重甲，只需要喺坦克上面射幾發火箭炮就夠，亦係城市戰步兵有優勢之處<br />\n步兵輕、快、靈活、隱密，根本就唔係機械可以代替，除非你係要炸咗個城市。"},{"pid":"154a9db5f918347ef155c2b3dc1e26a878891e15","tid":140740,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20